Sharon Clark https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sharon_Clark 0 Sharon Clark (born October 15, 1943, in Seminole, Oklahoma) is an American model and actress. She is Playboys Playmate of the Month for August 1970. Her centerfold was photographed by William Figge and Ed DeLong.
